plymouth (24.004.60-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release (Closes: #1059364)
  * debian/gbp.conf: Set upstream-vcs-tag
  * d/p/configure.ac-Avoid-embedding-the-date-in-the-version.patch: Dropped,
    autotools are gone
