plymouth (23.360.11-0ubuntu1) noble; urgency=medium

  * New upstream version 23.360.11
  * Refresh patches
  * Build using meson, autotools is not supported anymore
  * Do not pass SYSTEMD_ASK_PASSWORD_AGENT: now detected by upstream
  * Add new build dep libevdev
  * label-ft is now built from upstream as label-freetype.so
  * label.so is now label-pango.so
  * plymouth.docs: update upstream files
  * Update libplymouth5.symbols
  * spinfinity: do not use meson symlink
  * Fix systemdsystemunitdir to add missing /usr prefix
  * Cherry-pick upstream patch to prevent xkb_keymap crash

